Q)You are given a stream of integers. Find the first number greater than 10 using Streams?

🌴Ans) let's break it down.

✅️step 1) convert the list to stream

✅️step 2) call filter() with n-> n >10 for num greater than 10 .

✅️step 3) call findFirst() to get the first n >10 num .

🌴Example :
👇

List<Integer> numbers = Arrays.asList(5, 8, 11, 3, 15, 9);


Optional<Integer> firstNumber = numbers
 .stream()
 .filter(n -> n > 10)
 .findFirst();


🟣👉Output: {11}